# Audit CFG-02 — Docker build context is the repo root, and the service
# Dockerfiles reinstall dependencies + rebuild inside the image. Keep the
# following OUT of the build context so they never land in distributable
# image layers:
#   - a developer's real .env.local (secrets, also read by `next build`)
#   - host-native node_modules (Windows binaries polluting a Linux stage)
#   - prior build output and TS incremental caches
#   - the git history
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/npm-debug.log*
**/coverage
